OL,3,CCardiac arrest survivor urges people
OL,4,Cto know their nearest defibrillator
OL,6,FTom Fane from Fleet in Hampshire fell
OL,7,Fseriously ill earlier this year. His
OL,8,Fwife kept an eye on him at home, while
OL,9,Ftheir teenage son rushed out of the
OL,10,Fhouse to the local football club to
OL,11,Fpick up their defibrillator.
OL,13,FHe ended up on the bedroom floor and
OL,14,Fthanks to the emergency services
OL,15,Foperator guiding his wife and son how
OL,16,Fto administer CPR and where to get a
OL,17,Fdefibrillator he's alive today.
