OL,3,CCardiac arrest survivor urges people
OL,4,Cto know their nearest defibrillator
OL,6,F"I went into the bedroom and dad was
OL,7,Fon the floor with a fully purple
OL,8,Fhead," said his 18-year-old son,
OL,9,FFreddie.
OL,11,F"Mum was on the phone to the ambulance
OL,12,Fwith the operator telling her what to
OL,13,Fdo. But in the moment you just don't
OL,14,Fthink about anything, you do what you
OL,15,Fknow and are told."
OL,17,FFreddie was sent to the nearby
OL,18,Ffootball club in fleet to get the
OL,19,Fdefibrillator. Luckily he'd also been
OL,20,Fon a CPR course at Farnborough college
OL,21,Fwhere he studied.
