OL,3,CCardiac arrest survivor urges people
OL,4,Cto know their nearest defibrillator
OL,6,F"It was an easy machine to use. The
OL,7,Foperator gave us the code for it. It
OL,8,Fis a smart machine that counts down
OL,9,Fand is smart."
OL,11,F"The hospital said I had a major out
OL,12,Fof hospital cardiac arrest and I am
OL,13,Flucky to be here," said Mr Fane.
OL,15,F"First becuase of the CPR and second
OL,16,Fby the defibrillator Freddie got from
OL,17,FFleet FC."
OL,19,FThe family are now keen to spread the
OL,20,Fword of the importance of CPR and
OL,21,Fdefibrillators .
