OL,3,CCardiac arrest survivor urges people
OL,4,Cto know their nearest defibrillator
OL,6,F"We got him that first shot within six
OL,7,Fto seven minutes," said his wife,
OL,8,FAmanda. "The advice is find out where
OL,9,Fthe one near you is."
OL,11,FTom still has a way to go to make a
OL,12,Ffull recovery but will be forever
OL,13,Fthankful for the ambulance service,
OL,14,FFrimley Park Hospital and the action
OL,15,Fof his son and wife.
